<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa19">
<l>kuttu viḷakkeriya kōṭṭuk kāl kaṭṭil mēl</l>
<l>metteṉṟa pañca cayaṉattiṉ mēl ēṟik</l>
<l>kottalar pūṅkuḻal nappiṉṉai koṅkai mēl</l>
<l>vaittuk kiṭanta malar mārpā vāy tiṟavāy</l>
<l>mait taṭam kaṇṇiṉāy nī yuṉ maṇāḷaṉai</l>
<l>yettaṉai pōtum tuyileḻa voṭṭāy kāṇ</l>
<l>ettaṉaiyēlum pirivāṟṟakillāyāl</l>
<l>tattuvam aṉṟu takavēlōr empāvāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As the standing lamp shines, O You with a wide chest,</l>
<l>Who climbed upon the soft bed with five [qualities], on the cot with ivory legs,</l>
<l>and lay placing [Your head] on the breasts of Nappiṉṉai</l>
<l rend="indent">whose curly hair has blossoms that flower in clusters,</l>
<l>open [Your] mouth!</l>
<l>O You with big eyes [coloured with] kohl!</l>
<l>See, you will not allow Your Husband to wake from sleep even for a while!</l>
<l>Oh, you cannot bear separation even for a while!</l>
<l>[This] is not worthy of [Your] nature!</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
